{"tid":682874,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：北角閩港小廚","createTime":"2018-05-29T08:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T02:30:58.000Z","uid":181719,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a440942a3b382212657b548bece1f3c1f2fd23d4","tid":682874,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"炸雞卷、土筍凍，聽就聽得多，香港比較少地方有得食嘅，有一晚行北角發現呢間野，仲要10蚊件土筍凍咁平，就梗係入去試吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/161037_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F161037_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d3216aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來佢個形狀成舊砵仔糕咁，又整得幾有喜感，我諗其他地方嘅土筍凍唔係呢個形狀？其實成舊野係冇乜味嘅啫喱黎，靠少少醋黎提味（果然係冷盤吓），啲土筍口感似蜆肉，有好輕微嘅腥味啦，唔算係好食，但都過得去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/161110_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F161110_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f8c56a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞卷真係有啲失望，一直聽一位福建肥妹講話係好好食嘅野，其實只係肉碎撈馬蹄做餡嘅炸物黎，都足料嘅，不過口感唔豐富，食完會覺得酒樓嘅雞絲炸春卷先至係王道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/161124_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F161124_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d642af1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而因為想試多樣野，而同雞卷做雙拼嘅炸醋肉係幾特別。佢有啲似上海排骨嘅做法，但上海排骨咸而炸醋肉酸，醋味其實好中和到食炸物嘅膩感，所以食落幾清新。我諗如果可以同上海排骨撈埋黎食就好玩喇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/161146_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F161146_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ad6b9efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後嗌多個大路嘅炒粉絲做主食，炒得算有鑊氣，但都係唔夠味，要撈啲豆辦醬先好食，可能呢間野整體都係走清淡路線啦。"},{"pid":"578fdbf7ebe9cf60ad650a72ba5cba6ca0e37e78","tid":682874,"uid":39971,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"閪港小廚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e242dad2c64c1a18e28303267ee2f8cec2b9b71b","tid":682874,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"578fdbf7ebe9cf60ad650a72ba5cba6ca0e37e78","tid":682874,"uid":39971,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"閪港小廚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:32:02.000Z","msg":"呢個花名幾好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8b596a33681fc570d558e1d37e97858ba1a240","tid":682874,"uid":73160,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"住北角三年<br />\n你會知道福狗菜係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n全中國最垃圾菜系<br />\n<br />\n福建狗全部唔識食<br />\n錢就多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7817c666c190a2787c08d3f98891cc15c1f9655a","tid":682874,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e8b596a33681fc570d558e1d37e97858ba1a240","tid":682874,"uid":73160,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"住北角三年<br />\n你會知道福狗菜係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n全中國最垃圾菜系<br />\n<br />\n福建狗全部唔識食<br />\n錢就多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/an